nodes.text: The Vop Hui was a CR90 corvette used by the Rebel Alliance. The Vop Hui along with the Mar Duun attempted to disrupt a meeting involving TIE Defender prototypes being transferred to the Escort Carrier Hininbirg by deploying mines around the transfer point. However, the Vop Hui and the Mar Duun were destroyed along with the minefield by Imperial Ace Maarek Stele.
